---
title: One-Pot Beef, Pork & Chorizo Orecchiette with Mushrooms, Parmesan & Parsley
description: Brighten your day with another stunning pasta sauce. There are so many combinations you can try and this tomato-based one is a standout among them. Combine chorizo with hearty mushrooms, beef and pork to create that pasta sauce we can’t get enough of.
